<%= javascript_pack_tag 'main' %>
<%= csrf_meta_tag %>

<div class="poems-index-container bg-pMediumGreen text-pDarkGreen font-serif flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between">

   <div id="js-forks-container" class="main text-17 flex flex-row relative md:absolute md:pt-20 min-w-screen min-h-screen order-2">

      <%# div to duplicate w js %>
      <div class="js-intro-fork fork-holder" poem-id="0">
         <p class="mb-3">Intro Fork Title</p>
         <div>
            <p>Intro fork body</p>
            <p>Another line and <a href="2">two snakes</a></p>
            <p>Another <a href="1">one elephant</a></p>
            <p>One line <a href="2">two tigers</a></p>
         </div>
         <div>
            <p>JS TIMER TEST</p>
            <button id="start_timer">HOW LONG?</button>
         </div>
      </div>

   </div>

   <div class="breadcrumbs-drawer md:min-h-screen h-auto bg-pLightGreen drop-shadow-xl text-12 relative order-1">
      <span class="absolute top-6 right-6 md:hidden">1/<%= @total_number_of_poems %></span>
      <div class="hidden md:block total p-6 md:pt-20 border-b-1 border-pPurple">
         <p>You have visited 3 out of <%= @total_number_of_poems %> forks</p>
      </div>
      <div class="breadcrumbs p-6">
         <div class="js-breadcrumbs-container max-h-[54px] md:max-h-auto md:overflow-visible overflow-scroll mb-breadcrumbs-container flex md:flex-col flex-col-reverse">
            <%# tag to repeat %>
            <a href="">Original Fork</a>
         </div>
      </div>


      <div class="hidden">
         <%= @poems.each do |poem| %>
            <%= simple_form_for poem, url: poem_path(poem.id), remote: true, authenticity_token: true, method: :put do |f| %>
               <%= f.input :total_read_time, as: :numeric %>

               <%= f.button :submit %>
            <% end %>
         <% end %>
      
      </div>

      
   </div>

   <div class="metadata-drawer md:h-screen h-auto bg-pLightGreen drop-shadow-xl text-12 overflow-scroll order-3">
      <div class="date p-6 md:pt-20 border-b-1 border-pPurple flex md:flex-row flex-col justify-between">
         <div>
            <span>
               <%= Time.now.strftime(" %d %B %Y") %>
            </span>
            <span id="time"></span>
         </div>
         <div class="mt-3 md:mt-0">
            <span id="location"></span>
         </div>
      </div>

      <div class="meta p-6 border-b-1 border-pPurple">
         <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between mb-3">
            <div class="md:mb-0 mb-3">301 unique visits</div>
            <div>This fork has been read for <span class="js-fork-total-read-time"></span></div>
         </div>
         <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between">
            <div>1019 total visits</div>
            <div class="md:ml-3 md:mt-0 mt-3">Average of 4 mins 29 secs reading time per visit</div>
         </div>
      </div>

      <div class="links-to p-6 border-b-1 border-pPurple">
         <h3 class="text-17 mb-3">Other links to this fork</h3>
         <p><a href="">Link 1</a></p>
         <p><a href="">Link 2</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="comments p-6">
         <h3 class="text-17 mb-3">Comments</h3>
         <textarea name="" rows="7" id="comm-box" class="w-full text-12"></textarea>
         <button class="forks-button mt-3">post comment</button>

         <div class="post-comms mt-6 max-w-fit">
            <div class="single-comm mb-3">
               <p><span class="text-pPurple mr-1.5">01:21:39 30 January 2022</span>I’m not sure why, but this makes me feel like I’m the only one awake on a spaceship. It’s peaceful, but lonely. Filled with purpose, but melancholy. Direct, but subtle.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="single-comm mb-3">
               <p><span class="text-pPurple mr-1.5">22:48:35 17 April 2021</span>I don't know what this makes me feel but its not a normal feeling and I twitch every time the music completely goes off</p>
            </div>
            <div class="single-comm mb-3">
               <p><span class="text-pPurple mr-1.5">15:52:03 27 March 2021</span>This feels like you are the only one left on the planet walking through the car ridden streets, nobody in sight and you just keep walking without a sense of direction or time</p>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>

   </div>

</div>




